project.name: NSLondon
project.description: NSLondon is a free, volunteer-run community for developers building on Apple platforms. We host monthly meetups in London, sharing talks, demos, and opportunities to connect across the iOS/macOS development ecosystem. We have over 3000 members, but are entirely non-profit and volunteer run. Our website is open source and hosted via GitHub Pages to help make our events and resources accessible to the wider community.
